Package: SMRmix
Type: Package
Title: A Mixed Effect Similarity Matrix Regression Model (SMRmix) for Integrating Multiple Microbiome Datasets at Community Level
Version: 0.1.0
Description: This package provides implementation of SMRmix, which integrates heterogeneous microbiome datasets and tests the association between microbial composition and an outcome of interest.
Imports: stats, harmonicmeanp, lme4, nlme, MASS, expm
Suggests: rmarkdown, knitr, phyloseq, GUniFrac
Author: Mengyu He
